    "description": "REA India Holdings Services has an exciting opening for a Sales Manager at our Pune office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout REA India Holdings Services:\nREA India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Source and close property deals with prospective buyers and investors\n• Coordinate with legal teams for documentation and title verification\n• Conduct site visits and property presentations for clients\n• Liaise with banks and NBFCs for home loan assistance to customers\n• Coordinate with architects, contractors, and project teams\n• Manage relationships with existing customers post-purchase\n• Build relationships with channel partners and brokers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Property Management\n• Proficiency in Due Diligence\n• Proficiency in Sales Techniques\n• Proficiency in Portfolio Management\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in Market Research\n• Proficiency in RERA Compliance\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Pune, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with REA India Holdings Services!",
